# DXCTestCase
Steps to run the given python program:
Make sure python3 is installed. Then follow the below commands
 1) Open any IDE(Integrated Development Environment) i.e; Visual Studio or Pycharm or IDLE
 2) Open the python file provided in this repository in IDE
 3) Click on RUN
 4) It Will ask for the Input 
 5) Give any input and Press Enter
 6) It will show the 'Fibonacci Series' and the 'sum of the series' if the input is valid number
 7) If input is String it will alert you


Sample Input and Output:
=========================
INPUT1:
Enter a number:6

OUTPUT1:
0
1
1
2
3
5
And the sum of series is 12

INPUT2:
Enter a number:strig
OUTPUT2:
Given Input is string, Please Enter a Number

INPUT3:
Enter a number:-78
OUTPUT3:
Please enter a positive number
